Webex App | Select a virtual camera for calls or meetings
The right virtual camera software can turn a regular screenshare into a virtual presentation. Customize your background, add filters to your webcam stream, or stream multiple video sources at once. Virtual cameras show up in your camera options along with other hardware.
1
Join your meeting, then select or .
2
Under Camera, select your virtual camera from the list.

  Mac users: Virtual cameras may or may not be enabled by your system administrator.

  Camera options can also be managed prior to a call or meeting from your video settings.